</section><section id="vendors" class="panel admin-panel"><h2>업체목록</h2><form id="vendorForm" method="post" action="/admin/add/vendor" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="gridform"><input name="name" placeholder="업체명" required><select name="category"><%settings.categories.forEach(c=>{%><option><%=c%></option><%})%></select><select name="region"><%settings.regions.forEach(r=>{%><option><%=r%></option><%})%></select><input name="phone" placeholder="연락처"><input name="kakao_url" placeholder="카카오톡 문의 링크"><input name="tags" placeholder="태그"><input name="business_hours" placeholder="영업시간"><select name="status"><option value="active">노출</option><option value="pending">검수중</option><option value="hidden">숨김</option><option value="expired">광고만료</option></select><select name="ad_type"><option value="none">광고없음</option><option value="general">일반광고</option><option value="recommended">추천광고</option></select><input name="expire_at" type="date" placeholder="광고/배너 만기일"><label><input type="checkbox" name="banner_active"> 배너활성</label><select name="linked_user_id"><option value="">연결 회원 없음</option><% (users||[]).filter(u=>u.role!=='admin').forEach(u=>{%><option value="<%=u.id%>"><%=u.username%> / <%=u.nickname||'-'%></option><%})%></select><textarea name="description" placeholder="업체소개"></textarea><div class="image-guide"><b>대표 이미지/GIF 권장 규격</b><br>대표 이미지는 홈의 일반목록, 추천목록, 프리미엄배너에 공통으로 사용됩니다.<small>권장 크기 720 × 900px / 4:5 세로형 / JPG·PNG·WEBP·GIF / 최대 5MB 이하</small></div><input type="file" name="image" accept="image/*"><button>업체 등록</button></form>
